{"tid":1418970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"左膠有份幫藍衫斬路人，血債血償！！","createTime":"2019-08-05T22:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T10:41:50.000Z","uid":5350,"like":38,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cd4d8729b9cab32ac3aa7a12bc507736deaf1e77","tid":1418970,"uid":5350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:24:04.000Z","msg":"睇完隔離post之後嬲到仆街<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n荃灣嗰班阻住同藍衫開拖既左膠們 你地依家開心啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418913\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418913</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n你地班死左膠為咗實踐你地嘅「道德」「正義」<br />\n竟然去擋前線行動，保護周圍斬人嘅黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後另一邊就有人比黑社會斬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果冇你地阻住，前線一早擊退咗幾個黑社會。<br />\n仲有市民會比人斬？<br />\n<br />\n黑警保護𣎴義政權，係幫兇<br />\n左膠保護斬人嘅黑社會，都係幫兇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414219d6411902a7d13083ee82bb98f2ff40dae1","tid":1418970,"uid":5350,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:25:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PUTQ8Rt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPUTQ8Rt.png&h=925aa4f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a4c28508e70587221f0641693abb419bcad2db2","tid":1418970,"uid":5350,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:26:42.000Z","msg":"幫兇"},{"pid":"182b1607a84270c6a56f30e51daf858325ceade6","tid":1418970,"uid":296222,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:26:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"23634ddad116ae857a92bb79202a00cc6d12b186","tid":1418970,"uid":5350,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:27:03.000Z","msg":"幫兇同樣有罪"},{"pid":"69d9c88a75bab2ebf392398fc76bd3da13c5877e","tid":1418970,"uid":209050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:27:33.000Z",